  "ingredientsTitle": "Bestanddele",
  "ingredientGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "items": [
     "3 koppies mieliemeel <br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-023.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-023-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 023\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "3 koppies melk",
     "4 koppies water",
     "60ml botter",
     "1 pakkie spek ( bacon)",
     "1 ui in ringe gesny<br>",
     "30 ml olie<br>",
     "1 blikkie tamatie en uie mengsel<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-011.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-011-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 011\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "10 ml gemengde kruie<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-014.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-014-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 014\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "4 kaasworsies (as jy het, anders los jy dit uit)",
     "1 blik heelpit mielies<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-027.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-027-768x1024.jpg\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\" alt=\"pap blog 027\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>",
     "2 koppies gerasperde kaas van jou keuse<br>",
     "sout en peper"
    ]
   }
  ],
  "directionsTitle": "Metode",
  "directionGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "steps": [
     "Braai die uie in 30 ml olie.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-002.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-002.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 002\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Snipper die spek en braai saam met die uie.",
     "Sny die worsies in ringetjies en braai ook saam met spek.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-003.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-003.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 003\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Roer 10ml gemengde kruie en tamatie in blikkie by en kook deur vir 10 minute &#8211; hou nou die mengsel eenkant.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-016.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-016.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 016\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Verhit die melk en water in n kastrol.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-021.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-021.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 021\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Voeg die mieliemeel, sout en peper by en roer dat dit nie klonte maak nie &#8211; laat dit vir 15 minute prut.",
     "Roer die botter by die pap.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-030.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-030.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 030\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Roer die heelpitmielies in die pap.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-034.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-034.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 034\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Smeer n oondvaste bak en skep n lagie pap onder in die bak.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-037.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-037.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 037\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Gevolg deur n lagie spek en uie mengsel.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-038.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-038.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 038\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Gevolg deur n lagie kaas, herhaal die lagies nog een keer.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-041.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-041.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 041\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Eindig heel bo met n lagie kaas.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-046.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 046\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>",
     "Bak dit vir 40 minute by 180 grade celsius.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-047.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/pap-blog-047.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"pap blog 047\" title=\"Paptert - verby lekker\"></a>"
    ]
   }
  ],
  "notesTitle": "Notas",
  "notes": [
   "Jy kan enige vulsel gebruik waarvan jy hou.  Die spek kan vervang word met groente.  Ek het n anyskaas gebruik in die paptert.  Die keuse van die kaas berus ook op n persoonlike besluit.  Het die tert al met heerlike bloukaas gemaak."
  ],
  "videoHtml": null
 },
