   "avatar": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f19140ecf5b531edcab42d7f2d07c2fc5516ea5d729fc89d2f660757c2880626?s=96&d=mm&r=g",
   "date": "2023-04-13T08:56:45",
   "html": "<p>Ek het dit nog nooit gevries nie, maar ek glo dit sal vir redelik lank gevries kan word.</p>"
